comments: Tamara is very helpful, and goes out of her way to explain the assignments in more detail if needed. The work deadlines are spread out in a way that doesn\'t overwhelm you. If needed she will give you more time to complete projects, and the two tests have useful study guides. Overall, my experience was great in this class.
Very nice, helpful, and wonderful person.
Tamara is an extremely nice professor. Her class is really easy because of the way she teaches. She is clear and concise, and she is always willing to help her students outside of class.
